            "title": "油價升逾1%　花旗上調油價預測",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國際期油價格反彈逾1%，因美國和歐洲部分地區天氣寒冷，刺激冬季燃料需求。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-3.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-3.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油收報每桶73.92美元，升60美仙，升幅0.8%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">倫敦布蘭特期油收市報每桶76.92美元，升76美仙，升幅約1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">花旗上調今年首季布蘭特期油平均價格預測至每桶71美元，紐約期油上調至每桶67美元，其他季度則未有調整，主要反映市場憂慮即將上任美國總統的特朗普，或因收緊對伊朗制裁而影響原油供應；但維持對全年油價看跌的觀點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14625956-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be1%e3%80%80%e8%8a%b1%e6%97%97%e4%b8%8a%e8%aa%bf%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e9%a0%90%e6%b8%ac",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-4.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-01-10 08:45:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐股個別發展  德股回軟  資源股向好",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲主要股市收市個別發展。泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市反彈0.42%，報515點，資源股升1.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230711-094813_20191028_EuropeStock_AP_source-ap_-1-1-1-1-1-2-2.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230711-094813_20191028_EuropeStock_AP_source-ap_-1-1-1-1-1-2-2.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國DAX指數收市報20317點，跌12點，跌幅0.06%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數報7490點，升37點，升幅0.51%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數報8319點，升68點，升幅0.83%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國超市Tesco及馬莎百貨(M&amp;S)的銷售表現欠佳，股價應聲曾挫逾4%及8%，Tesco收市挽回大部分失地，馬莎百貨跌勢仍維持；兩者均提到英國經濟正面臨挑戰，工資稅上升同時推高營運成本。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14625950-%e6%ad%90%e8%82%a1%e5%80%8b%e5%88%a5%e7%99%bc%e5%b1%95-%e5%be%b7%e8%82%a1%e5%9b%9e%e8%bb%9f-%e8%b3%87%e6%ba%90%e8%82%a1%e5%90%91%e5%a5%bd",
